prompt: Show me the curriculum for BS Computer Science.
response:
Here is the curriculum for BS Computer Engineering. In the first year, first semester, you will have CHEM 21.31, CHEM 21.32, ENGG 30.02, ENGL 11, FILI 12, INTACT 11, MATH 10, PATHFit 1, SocSc 11, and THEO 11. In the first year, second semester, you will have ENGG 11, ENLIT 12, FILI 11, FLC 11, HISTO 11, INTACT 12, MATH 30.23, PATHFit 2, PHYS 31.31, and PHYS 31.32.

For the second year, there is a summer term with ENGG 21 and MATH 30.24. The first semester includes ENGG 101.01, ENGG 101.02, ENGG 170, ENGG 24, ENGG 25, ENGG 31, HISTO 12, PATHFit 3, and PHILO 11. The second semester includes ENGG 102.01, ENGG 102.02, ENGG 111.01, ENGG 111.02, ENGG 16.22, ENGG 171.20, ENGG 32, NSTP 11, PATHFit 4, STS 10, SocSc 12, and THEO 12.

For the third year, first semester includes ArtAp 10, ENGG 121.01, ENGG 121.02, ENGG 161, ENGG 27.01, IE 1, IE 2, NSTP 12, PHILO 12, and SocSc 13. The second semester includes ENGG 122.01, ENGG 122.02, ENGG 125.03, ENGG 151.01, ENGG 151.02, ENGG 192, ENGG 38, PHILO 13, and THEO 13.

For the fourth year, there is a summer term with ENGG 197. The first semester includes ENGG 123.01, ENGG 123.02, ENGG 142.20, ENGG 143.01, ENGG 143.02, ENGG 152.01, ENGG 18X.XX-1 (IE 4), ENGG 199.1, and SocSc 14. The second semester includes DLQ 10, ENGG 124.01, ENGG 124.02, ENGG 126, ENGG 156, ENGG 190, ENGG 199.2, and IE 3.

Finally, for the fifth year, first semester includes ENGG 160, ENGG 168, ENGG 178.20, ENGG 189, ENGG 18X.XX-2, and ENGG 18X.XX-3.
